data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Van Buren! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, built in 2022, seamlessly blends modern elegance with comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of vinyl plank flooring that not only adds a touch of sophistication but is also easy to maintain. The heart of this home lies in the kitchen, boasting beautiful granite countertops that provide both style and durability. Imagine preparing delicious meals in this well-appointed space, where the blend of aesthetics and functionality creates a culinary haven. The open layout ensures seamless interaction with the adjoining living and dining areas, perfect for entertaining friends and family.  Discover a covered patio that extends the living space outdoors. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a summer barbecue, this space is an inviting retreat. The four bedrooms provide ample space for a growing family or the flexibility to create a home office or hobby room.  With its prime location in the heart of Van Buren, you'll enjoy the convenience of being close to local amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully crafted home yours.
